snippet.title: Pre-Calculus - Solve a linear equation that has no solution
snippet.description: This video shows an example of a linear equation that has no solution.  Note how the variables drop away entirely and the statement left over is completely false.  That is the clue there is no solution.  For more videos please visit http://www.mysecretmathtutor.com
